          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".93V U-235 metal disc in cadmium box on the 0 degree",
                " axis of the beam.",
                ".Discs were 15 mm in diam and 0.125 mm thick.",
                ".Isotopic composition was found by mass-spectrometry",
                " to be",
                "  U-234      1.138  atom %",
                "  U-235     91.097  atom %",
                "  U-236      2.034  atom %",
                "  U-238      5.731  atom %",
                ".about 2 grams were used for each irradiation.",
                ".The uranium discs were spaced by gold discs."
              ]
            }
          ],
